text: Teo Bielefeld (born September 11, 1965) is an American rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Berkeley, California
